Barbara McCauley ( b . Southern California , USA ) is a popular romance writer . She has written over 35 romance novels for Harlequin Enterprises since 1991 . McCauley was born in Southern California as the youngest of five children . She is currently married and has two children . She published her first book in 1991 , Woman Tamer . She is now co - president of the Orange County chapter of Romance Writers of America . 